Summary[edit]

DescriptionFlag of Kosovo GovOutline PD.svg
English: Outline of Kosovo is according to the document published by The Office of Prime Minister of the Republic of Kosovo. Colors are RGB approximations from the same document (which is in CYMK). Additionally, a non-Public Domain version from Wikimedia commons was used as a reference for sizing and placing of elements.
